            <title>[CASSANDRA-7493] Remove traces of rows_per_partition_to_cache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7493</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6745&quot; title=&quot;Require specifying rows_per_partition_to_cache&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6745&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6745&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changed the way we configure how many rows per partition we cache, some old stuff was left in, clear it out&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12725257">CASSANDRA-7493</key>
            <summary>Remove traces of rows_per_partition_to_cache</summary>
